        ⁡
        
          (
          
            
              
                n
                π
                x
              
              L
            
          
          )
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle e_{n}(x)={\sqrt {\frac {2}{L}}}\sin \left({\frac {n\pi x}{L}}\right)}
  for n ≥ 1 are eigenfunctions of Δ. Indeed,

  
    
      
        Δ
        
          e
          
            n
          
        
        =
        −
        
          
            
              
