    {\displaystyle \Phi (x,t):=(4t\pi )^{-{\frac {n}{2}}}\exp \left(-{\frac {|x|^{2}}{4t}}\right).}
  Notice that 

  
    
      
        
          d
          i
          a
          m
        
        (
        
